C>1
p(t)=a_0+a_1 t+\dots +a_n t^n
|a_0|+|a_1|+\dots + |a_n| \le C \sup_{t\in[0,1]} |p(t)|
\begin{align} p(t)&=1-t+t^2-t^3+\cdots+t^{2N-2}-t^{2N-1}\\ &=(1-t)(1+t^2+t^4+\cdots+t^{2N-2})\\ &=(1-t){1-t^{2N}\over1-t^2}\\ &={1-t^{2N}\over1+t} \end{align}
\sup_{t\in[0,1]}|p(t)|\le1
|a_0|+|a_1|+\cdots=1+1+\cdots=2N
C
N
C\lt2N
